column4: NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "C6B752A24599AE64CF8A4786FA090D8A", "I hear a voice coming from behind. The voice is...!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "345C4D884C417DB31622EA98765024A6", "I\'m impressed. You found the New Ogre Fortress!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "F1AD6FAA43B5F41A50F398BF75244AFB", "I won\'t let you do that! You\'d better get out of this cave!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "229CC1A944DC57EA802AF591C9E08850", "Master WaruSeadramon! Go ahead and do it, please!")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "4D8CDCAD453CA8F4F90DE88928EE96C1", "Come to the city and work, so you can repay your sins.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "69B9A30847B9A026A661E98DA7435026", "Alright, got it. I\'ll go to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "FF4D835749D3C0B369BBAE94AC1411A2", "Well, we got the cave back. I guess it\'s OK.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "D4DB52CF418FFE9E4A04B4A5B7715BD6", "I think this cave is OK now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "5228B18941FA0693BAE775BB48A34793", "You seem to be a really nice person. I\'m sure they\'ll realize their mistake someday.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "965527E547FAF6928E01118BA5E9B5BC", "I\'ll give you my treasure. It\'s in the back.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "25B612224C664B79219C018C7535F0A1", "Wait, wait. That\'s your treasure, right? I can\'t accept it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "905511714C29D8FF79EC31936688F0EC", "No, I don\'t need it. I want to go to your city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "9480472743B3B160BFB151BB442ADFB4", "Then what did we have to get this cave back for? For nothing...?")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "C5F80BBE45014E86600F61809B8DAB16", "I\'m sorry, but I really want to help you now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[CF70D2A3442829DE785A469051BB401B]", "0C716AB3412120ABB0AF448CCE763C20", "I\'m going straight to the city. I\'ll give you a ride if you want.")
